      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "PopAI's presentation engine is powered by what they call a \"Fast and Smart AI Presentation Agent,\" and 16 million users have already made it their go-to tool. Here's what sets it apart:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Theme Library",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Over dozens of professionally designed themes spanning categories like Business & Finance, Marketing, Education, and Culture & Arts. The \"Minimal Blue Aesthetic\" theme alone has been used 135,248 times—it's clean, versatile, and looks expensive.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Custom Template Upload",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Already have brand guidelines? Upload your own PowerPoint template, and PopAI will generate slides that match your corporate identity. No more off-brand presentations sneaking into meetings.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "PowerPoint Mode",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": PopAI exports directly to .pptx format, so you can fine-tune in PowerPoint if needed. This compatibility matters when you're collaborating with teams who live in Microsoft's ecosystem.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I recently needed a 15-slide deck for a client proposal. I typed three sentences about what I wanted, selected a theme, and had a complete presentation in under 40 seconds. The content was structured logically, the design was polished, and I only needed minor tweaks to the talking points.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
