            "text": ", and PopAI doesn't just skim the surface. It grasps relationships between sections, remembers details from earlier pages, and answers follow-up questions accurately. I tested this with a dense legal contract—it correctly identified termination clauses, payment schedules, and liability limits without me specifying page numbers.",
