            "text": "For many workflows, yes. PopAI handles conversational AI tasks, document analysis, presentation design, and data visualization in one platform. While specialized tools like Canva offer deeper design customization, PopAI's all-in-one approach eliminates the need to switch between multiple apps for most professional tasks.",
